  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Light Endoscopic Robot evaluation in abdominal and urological laparoscopic surgery : surgery
      with surgeon and robot (REL group = new treatment) versus surgery with surgeon and assistant
      (AO group - standard treatment)

      Primary outcome measure : Number of useful hands (light endoscopic robot = one useful
      mechanical hand)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
